{"title_page": "Bhawana Jha", "text_new": "{{short description|Indian politician (born 1973)}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| name          = Bhawana Jha\n| term_end3     = \n| year          = \n| date          = \n| footnotes     = \n| website       = \n| spouse        = \n| death_place   = \n| death_date    = \n| residence     = \n| birth_place   = \n| birth_date    = {{birth date and age|1973|12|03|df=yes}}\n| party         = [[Indian National Congress]]\n| term_start3   = \n| office        = [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]]\n| term_end2     = \n| term_start2   = \n| successor1    = \n| predecessor1  = \n| term_end1     = \n| term_start1   = \n| office1       = \n| predecessor   = \n| primeminister = \n| constituency  = [[Benipatti (Vidhan Sabha constituency)]]\n| term_end      = 2020\n| term_start    = 2015\n| source        = \n| image         = Bhawana Jha with Rahul Gandhi.jpg\n| caption       = Bhawna Jha with [[Rahul Gandhi]]\n}}\n\n'''Bhawana Jha''' is an Indian politician and the current member of [[Bihar Legislative Assembly]] from [[Benipatti (Vidhan Sabha constituency)]]. <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://vidhansabha.bih.nic.in/Knowyourmla.html|title=BIHAR VIDHAN SABHA/Know your MLA|website=vidhansabha.bih.nic.in|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hindi.news18.com/news/bihar/madhubani-mla-bhavna-jha-big-allegation-on-vikassheel-insan-party-vip-candidate-from-madhubani-nodvkj-2042428.html|title=MLA \u092d\u093e\u0935\u0928\u093e \u091d\u093e \u0915\u093e \u092c\u0921\u093c\u093e \u0906\u0930\u094b\u092a, \u092e\u0927\u0941\u092c\u0928\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 VIP \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0924\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0936\u0940 \u0928\u0947 \u0916\u0930\u0940\u0926\u093e \u0925\u093e \u091f\u093f\u0915\u091f|date=1970-01-01|website=News18 India|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.patrika.com/patna-news/bihar-congress-mla-bhavna-jha-took-selfie-on-bus-accident-sopt-2338245/|title=\u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u0916\u092c\u0930, 